# {{lb|en|biology}} A [[round#Adjective|round]] [[lump#Noun|lump]] made up of or [[coat#Verb|coated]] with [[slime#Noun|slime]] or a [[slimelike|slime-like]] [[substance]] such as [[mucus]].
